      <p>
        <inline name="agenda item name">Strengthening of the coordination of humanitarian and disaster relief assistance of the United Nations, including special economic assistance: strengthening of international cooperation and coordination of efforts to study, mitigate and minimize the consequences of the Chernobyl disaster</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 16 May 2023</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#noMainCommittee">[without reference to a Main Committee (<inline name="originating document">A/77/L.66</inline>)]</docProponent>
